33:05.570 --> 33:08.774
So if you can do something above and beyond, by all means, do it.

33:09.135 --> 33:11.278
You say, so your whole service am I giving money?

33:11.478 --> 33:11.738
No.

33:12.519 --> 33:16.384
No, the sermon is about don't miss out on what God is doing, because God's doing it.

33:17.005 --> 33:19.388
